  "description": "Nestled on a secluded beach surrounded by lush foliage, Casa Marina Resort, A Waldorf Astoria is just minutes from a lively downtown scene. It is close to shops, bars, water sports and national monuments. The hotel has easy access to world-class water sports, including deep-sea fishing, wind surfing, and diving in America\\'s only living barrier reef.Delight in the 311 guest rooms and suites at the beachfront hotel, where you\\'ll feel a historical sense of time and a cozy sense of place.Savour tantalizing seafood and tropical salads at the Casa Marina Resort, A Waldorf Astoria\\'s Sun-Sun Beach Bar & Grill featuring an open-air wood pavilion and an extraordinary view of the sea.Nestled on the island\\'s largest private beach, the inviting Casa Marina Resort, A Waldorf Astoria wedding location offers an intimate setting for wedding celebrations, honeymoons, anniversaries, and receptions. Take a refreshing morning dip in the oceanfront pool or whirlpool and drop by the fitness club for a vigorous workout.",
